Name: University 2.0
Notes: New library of lessons covering everything from layout and typography to interactions and 3D transforms

Name: Clean Up IX2
Notes: Clean your interactions panel up by bulk selecting and removing all unused interactions and animations

Name: A11Y Elements
Notes: Most commonly used elements and components are now keyboard and screen reader accessible

Name: Buy Now button
Notes: Buy Now checkout option for your Ecommerce store lets your customers check out faster

Name: Bulk delete Assets
Notes: Select multiple (or all) of your assets at once in the wide view of the asset manager to delete unneeded files.

Name: Printful Integration
Notes: Connect your Webflow Ecommerce store to Printful to get a print-on-demand store.

Name: Digital goods ᵇ
Notes: Add links to file downloads to any of your products.

Name: Shippo integration
Notes: Keep your Ecommerce orders synced in Shippo, easily create shipping labels, and automate order tracking for your customers.

Name: Nested Collection Lists
Notes: Nest a ‘child’ collection list into a ‘parent’ to display categories, tags — or any referenced content — in your designs.

Name: 3 larger breakpoints
Notes: Customize your designs for larger screens with 3 new device breakpoints at 1280px, 1440px, and 1920px.

Name: Ecomm. Email mgmt
Notes: Manage emails for your Ecommerce customers and team.

Name: Object-fit support
Notes: Control image resizing within elements using object-fit.

Name: No Shipping Checkout
Notes: Simplify checkout for orders that don’t need shipping.

Name: Canvas zoom
Notes: Resize the Designer canvas to preview site on larger screens.

Name: Custom easing curves for IX
Notes: Set custom easing curves for each step of your interactions.
